底，企圖為香港大陸化，取消港幣作鋪路。但此舉顯然將破壞香港金融地位。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.epochtimes.com/news/2019-08-18/60410577\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.epochtimes.com%2Fnews%2F2019-08-18%2F60410577&d=V4yVQ1MiaEIlcmjbsyBqFwogPkW5zMkxdNnzPoGklno%3D&h=52d1d5eb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.epochtimes.com/news/2019-08-18/60410577</a>"},{"pid":"0400264951d4a111b85e51a46b6aec4a5773173d","tid":1931703,"uid":1086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a044d4ed5e627e2fba2e7574e7dd68e487fececc","tid":1931703,"uid":33783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T09:59:29.000Z","msg":"跟樓主<br />\n天日大手入100手<br />\n仲唔發達<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T10:03:44.000Z","msg":"匯豐可以長期持有的優質股，已經處於合理偏平區域，建議分注買入，同時保持現金，等待機會<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/solution.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a14e59c383d8d69d79862a3618cdd896a5f5076","tid":1931703,"uid":5178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4c8647cd3b008d5a7943cb4cef31274694e6f833","tid":1931703,"uid":169869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T10:01:35.000Z","msg":"果4千億拎得返就係<br />\n<br />\n18/8/2019<br />\n香港金融圈盛傳，匯豐銀行先前向中國貸款高達4000億美元，用做中國外匯存底，數字直逼香港整體外匯4378億元，幾乎「掏空」香港，一旦屬實，中共企圖主導匯豐目的浮上檯面，一是因應港人擠兌，進行資本管控，二是掌握香港外匯存底，企圖為香港大陸化，取消港幣作鋪路。但此舉顯然將破壞香港金融地位。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.epochtimes.com/news/2019-08-18/60410577\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.epochtimes.com%2Fnews%2F2019-08-18%2F60410577&d=V4yVQ1MiaEIlcmjbsyBqFwogPkW5zMkxdNnzPoGklno%3D&h=52d1d5eb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.epochtimes.com/news/2019-08-18/60410577</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T10:08:05.000Z","msg":"佢地而家咪用緊個4000億掃貨囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f6c05e15bb5833c889269cfd925e3b6d2cd5332","tid":1931703,"uid":108337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T10:09:22.000Z","msg":"留名